        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Last encounter with her? She pulls her consciousness from her shattered body, the last flicker of sight fixed on that magician\\'s top hat.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 15,
        "ActionId": 15,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'In a forceful, almost imperious voice, she challenges him—demanding greater chances born from greater risks.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 16,
        "ActionId": 16,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Those nebulous possibilities lie far beyond reach, like a former life sealed away beneath dense, mundane burdens in a crimson dreamscape.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 17,
        "ActionId": 17,
        "NextActionId": null,
