        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": 1000.0,
        "Params": "{1: '999', 2: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory999.jpg', 3: '0', 4: '1', 5: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 41,
        "ActionId": 41,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '501118'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 42,
        "ActionId": 42,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "DialogEnable",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Lilith', 3: 'Even the Ascension-Network can reclaim the very strength it once granted—wouldn\\'t you agree?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 43,
        "ActionId": 43,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Lilith murmurs, lost in thought, but it\\'s clear she isn\\'t really directing the question at anyone around her.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 44,
        "ActionId": 44,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lilith', 3: 'But I\\'m not really interested in her. The one who fascinates me is that other Ascendant—the one who \"broke away\" from Babylonia.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 45,
        "ActionId": 45,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'She keeps talking, almost absentmindedly, as though she\\'s happy to fill the silence with small talk while we walk.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 46,
        "ActionId": 46,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lilith', 3: 'You know something, Little Lithos?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 47,
        "ActionId": 47,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Lilith turns to regard the slight figure at her side.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 48,
        "ActionId": 48,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lilith', 3: 'Project Cthylla, Project Winter... all that past suffering gave us strength. Yet we remain the victims of those reckless experiments.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 49,
        "ActionId": 49,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lilith', 3: 'Whether it\\'s forging a body mighty enough to withstand anything or blending our meager minds into a single force—either way, these are humanity\\'s paths to surviving the long winter.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 50,
        "ActionId": 50,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lilith', 3: 'What they once called \"winter\" begins as interstellar colonization and later takes the shape of the Punishing Virus. At one point, the promise of shielding everyone from this winter is so alluring it almost deceives all of us—every last one, the so-called \"cost of progress\".', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 51,
        "ActionId": 51,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lilith', 3: '...We\\'ve been pushed so far that we\\'ve nearly lost the ability to recognize our deepest desires.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 52,
        "ActionId": 52,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lilith', 3: 'But now we all realize that instead of fighting against it... laying ourselves bare before the storm is how we endure.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 53,
        "ActionId": 53,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 202,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 54,
        "ActionId": 54,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500514', 4: '400'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 55,
        "ActionId": 55,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '2', 2: '501118', 4: '-400'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 56,
        "ActionId": 56,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Lithos', 3: '...I appreciate what you did for the person I used to be, Lilith. At least now, we stand together again.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 57,
        "ActionId": 57,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'He doesn\\'t give a straight answer, only murmurs a soft, general agreement.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 58,
        "ActionId": 58,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lilith', 3: 'There\\'s no need for such formality.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 59,
        "ActionId": 59,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lilith', 3: 'That defector, however—she appears to have chosen an entirely different path...', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 60,
        "ActionId": 60,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lilith', 3: 'And I\\'m certain that when the time is right, she returns to that far northern realm.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 61,
        "ActionId": 61,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Lilith\\'s voice all but trembles with excitement.'}"
    },
